n\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Fintype/Card.html#Fintype.card\">Fintype.card</a> <span class=\"fn\">ι</span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HSub.hSub\">-</a> <span class=\"fn\">k</span>)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"Controlling the norm of `f.iteratedFDeriv` when `f` is continuous multilinear. For the same\nbound on the iterated derivative of `f` in the calculus sense,\nsee `ContinuousMultilinearMap.norm_iteratedFDeriv_le`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap.norm_iteratedFDeriv_le'","kind":"theorem","line":1320,"name":"ContinuousMultilinearMap.norm_iteratedFDeriv_le'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Multilinear/Basic.lean#L1320-L1333"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap.iteratedFDeriv\"><span class=\"name\">ContinuousMultilinearMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">iteratedFDeriv</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ι</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ι</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> wE₁</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">G</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> wG}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Field/Basic.html#NontriviallyNormedField\">NontriviallyNormedField</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#SeminormedAddCommGroup\">SeminormedAddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Basic.html#NormedSpace\">NormedSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#SeminormedAddCommGroup\">SeminormedAddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Basic.html#NormedSpace\">NormedSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Fintype/Defs.html#Fintype\">Fintype</a> <span class=\"fn\">ι</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap\">ContinuousMultilinearMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">k</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap\">ContinuousMultilinearMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">(fun (<span class=\"fn\">x</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Fin\">Fin</a> <span class=\"fn\">k</span></span>) =&gt; <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span>)</span> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The `k`-th iterated derivative of a continuous multilinear map `f` at the point `x`. It is a\ncontinuous multilinear map of `k` vectors `v₁, ..., vₖ` (with the same type as `x`), mapping them\nto `∑ f (x₁, (v_{i₁})₂, x₃, ...)`, where at each index `j` one uses either `xⱼ` or one\nof the `(vᵢ)ⱼ`, and each `vᵢ` has to be used exactly once.\nThe sum is parameterized by the embeddings of `Fin k` in the index type `ι` (or, equivalently,\nby the subsets `s` of `ι` of cardinality `k` and then the bijections between `Fin k` and `s`).\n\nThe fact that this is indeed the iterated Fréchet derivative is proved in\n`ContinuousMultilinearMap.iteratedFDeriv_eq`.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap.iteratedFDeriv","kind":"def","line":1306,"name":"ContinuousMultilinearMap.iteratedFDeriv","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Multilinear/Basic.lean#L1306-L1318"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap.norm_iteratedFDerivComponent_le\"><span class=\"name\">ContinuousMultilinearMap</span>.<span class=\"name\">norm_iteratedFDerivComponent_le</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ι</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> v}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ι</span> → <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> wE₁</span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">G</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> wG}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Field/Basic.html#NontriviallyNormedField\">NontriviallyNormedField</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#SeminormedAddCommGroup\">SeminormedAddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Basic.html#NormedSpace\">NormedSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span>)</span></span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#SeminormedAddCommGroup\">SeminormedAddCommGroup</a> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Module/Basic.html#NormedSpace\">NormedSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Fintype/Defs.html#Fintype\">Fintype</a> <span class=\"fn\">ι</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Fintype/Defs.html#Fintype\">Fintype</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">f</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/Module/Multilinear/Basic.html#ContinuousMultilinearMap\">ContinuousMultilinearMap</a> <span class=\"fn\">𝕜</span> <span class=\"fn\">E₁</span> <span class=\"fn\">G</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Set/Defs.html#Set\">Set</a> <span class=\"fn\">ι</span></span>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n