=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">c</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a>)</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">(∀ (<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>), <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">ε</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span>)</span> → <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <span class=\"fn\">m</span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LE.le\">≤</a> <span class=\"fn\">C</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">∏ <span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>, <a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">m</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a></span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ι</span>) → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">E</span> <span class=\"fn\">i</span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/Normed/Group/Defs.html#Norm.norm\">‖</a><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">f</span> <